[[San Francisco Giants]], [[Texas Rangers (baseball)|Texas Rangers]], and [[Chicago Cubs]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wfaa.com/story/sports/high-school/2014/08/21/14219360/ |title=Allen's Kyler Murray follows in dad's footsteps at A&M |date=May 28, 2014 |website=WFAA |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209210209/http://www.wfaa.com/story/sports/high-school/2014/08/21/14219360/ |archive-date=December 9, 2014 |access-date=May 6, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dallasnews.com/sports/high-schools/football-news/headlines/20131116-kevin-murray-has-gone-from-one-time-am-star-to-dallas-fort-worth-s-elite-quarterback-coach-with-a-client-list-to-prove-he-may-be-the-best.ece|title=Kevin Murray has gone from one-time A&M star to Dallas-Fort Worth's elite quarterback coach|work=dallasnews.com|accessdate=May 6, 2015}}</ref> Murray is a second-generation [[Korean American]], with his maternal grandmother being a South Korean national.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://usatodayhss.com/2014/gatorade-football-poy-kyler-murray-qa |title=Kyler Murray dishes about his dodgeball, The Streak and being a road warrior |date=December 8, 2014 |website=USA Today High School Sports |access-date=December 27, 2018}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of quarterbacks with non-white or non-black ancestry]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{footballstats|nfl=2562382|espn=3917315|pfr=M/MurrKy00}}\n{{baseballstats|mlb=663470|espn=41185|brm=murray001kyl}}\n*[http://www.soonersports.com/ViewArticle.dbml?ATCLID=211452796&DB_OEM_ID=31000 Oklahoma Sooners bio]\n*[https://www.azcardinals.com/team/players-roster/kyler-murray/ Arizona Cardinals bio]\n\n{{Arizona Cardinals roster navbox}}\n{{NFL starting quarterbacks navbox}}\n{{Navboxes| list1=\n{{Texas A&M Aggies quarterback navbox}}\n{{Oklahoma Sooners quarterback navbox}}\n{{Heisman Trophy}}\n{{Davey O'Brien Award}}\n{{AP Players of the Year}}\n{{Manning Award}}\n{{Earl Campbell Tyler Rose Award}}\n{{Big 12 Conference 